# Keep the Docker build context (repo root, used by winbuild/Dockerfile) lean:
# the image only needs the rdedup/ sources (for `cargo fetch`) and
# winbuild/build.sh. Excluding build artifacts and caches stops a multi-GB
# compiled target/ and the local venv/git history from being sent to the daemon
# or baked into the image. (Docker honors only this context-root .dockerignore.)
.git/
.venv/
**/target/
**/__pycache__/
*.so
*.pyd
*.pyo
*.pyc
out/
.pytest_cache/
